node.text: Iceberg wedges with aubergine cream and super crunchy topping. The last in my outdoor series, and what a perfect sunny week for it! Iceberg makes a great base for building layers of flavour and texture. One of my favourite lettuces, contrary to popular opinion. Find the recipe in FLAVOUR or at my link in bio.

node.text:
So… the #OTK, our very own Ottolenghi Test Kitchen, is joining Youtube!! Our first video is coming out this Thursday, in a brand new jam-packed series called ‘OTK: What’s for Dinner?’ 

@noorishbynoor @verenalochmuller @thechayamaya @gitaif @tara.wigley and I will be sharing a whole load of recipes from the new book, OTK: Shelf Love.. Plus, there’ll be a glimpse into how we test the dishes at the OTK, and we’ll answer some of your cooking questions too! 

Please subscribe, join us, and see some delicious things happen. Find the channel at my link in bio, or search Ottolenghi Test Kitchen on Youtube. 

Huge thanks to @tomwalkerfilm and his team, who just let us do our thing and somehow, magically, captured the best bits on camera.
